{"iti24:0.1":"Itivuttaka 24 ","iti24:0.2":"Ekakanipata ","iti24:0.3":"Tatiyavagga ","iti24:0.4":"Atthipunjasutta ","iti24:1.1":"Vuttanhetam bhagavata vuttamarahatati me sutam: ","iti24:2.1":"“Ekapuggalassa, bhikkhave, kappam sandhavato samsarato siya evam maha atthikankalo atthipunjo atthirasi yathayam vepullo pabbato, sace samharako assa, sambhatanca na vinasseyya”ti. ","iti24:2.2":"Etamattham bhagava avoca. ","iti24:2.3":"Tatthetam iti vuccati: ","iti24:3.1":"“Ekassekena kappena, ","iti24:3.2":"puggalassatthisancayo; ","iti24:3.3":"Siya pabbatasamo rasi, ","iti24:3.4":"iti vuttam mahesina. ","iti24:4.1":"So kho panayam akkhato, ","iti24:4.2":"vepullo pabbato maha; ","iti24:4.3":"Uttaro gijjhakutassa, ","iti24:4.4":"magadhanam giribbaje. ","iti24:5.1":"Yato ca ariyasaccani, ","iti24:5.2":"sammappannaya passati; ","iti24:5.3":"Dukkham dukkhasamuppadam, ","iti24:5.4":"dukkhassa ca atikkamam; ","iti24:5.5":"Ariyancatthangikam maggam, ","iti24:5.6":"dukkhupasamagaminam. ","iti24:6.1":"Sa sattakkhattum paramam, ","iti24:6.2":"sandhavitvana puggalo; ","iti24:6.3":"Dukkhassantakaro hoti, ","iti24:6.4":"sabbasamyojanakkhaya”ti. ","iti24:7.1":"Ayampi attho vutto bhagavata, iti me sutanti. ","iti24:7.2":"Catuttham. "}